2012.11.9 KYOCERA Corporation

●ビルド手順
1. Code Aurora Forum (CAF) よりBase環境をDownloadする。
    https://www.codeaurora.org/

    Manifest Fileは以下になります。
    https://www.codeaurora.org/xwiki/bin/QAEP/
    <Releases on release branch>
     August 28, 2012  M8960AAAAANLYA1732  msm8960  release  M8960AAAAANLYA1732.xml

    $ repo init -u git://codeaurora.org/platform/manifest.git -b release -m M8960AAAAANLYA1732.xml --repo-url=git://codeaurora.org/tools/repo.git
    $ repo sync

        注）Download方法及び不明点の詳細はCAFをご参照ください。

2. kernelフォルダを、1.でDownloadした環境に上書きします。

3. 環境変数PATHにJava Development Kit (JDK) のpathを追加します。
    $ export PATH=<JDKのInstallPath>/bin:$PATH

4. 下記Commandを実行します。
    $ source build/envsetup.sh
    $ choosecombo release msm8960 user
    $ make clean && make BOARD_USES_SRS_TRUEMEDIA:=false BOARD_HAS_ATH_WLAN_AR6004:=false WIFI_DRIVER_DEF_CONF_FILE:="/system/etc/wifi/WCNSS_qcom_cfg.ini" BOARD_KERNEL_CMDLINE:=console=ttyHSL0,115200,n8 no_console_suspend=1 androidboot.hardware=qcom user_debug=31 msm_rtb.filter=0x3F ehci-hcd.park=3 maxcpus=2 BOARD_BOOTIMAGE_PARTITION_SIZE:=0x00800000 BOARD_RECOVERYIMAGE_PARTITION_SIZE:=0x02800000 BOARD_SYSTEMIMAGE_PARTITION_SIZE:=1006632960 BOARD_USERDATAIMAGE_PARTITION_SIZE:=11022630912 BOARD_PERSISTIMAGE_PARTITION_SIZE:=8388608 BOARD_CACHEIMAGE_PARTITION_SIZE:=209715200 BOARD_DELTAIMAGE_PARTITION_SIZE:=687865856 BOARD_TOMBSTONESIMAGE_PARTITION_SIZE:=402653184 BOARD_SECURITYIMAGE_PARTITION_SIZE:=8388608 BOARD_HAS_ATH_ETH_ALX:=false KERNEL_DEFCONFIG:=msm8960_defconfig -j8

    Note:最後の"-j8"はBuild環境に合わせて変更ください。

以上
